identify` - check which username the user has registered to hubot brain\n\n* `hubot identify {untappd username}` - set untappd user name that will be used for user feed polling\n\n* `hubot last {n} beers` - shows the last `n` beers you had, default `n` is 1","maintainers":[{"name":"spoike","email":"mishakun+npm@gmail.com"}],"time":{"modified":"2015-01-22T22:11:43.680Z","created":"2015-01-22T22:11:43.680Z","0.0.1":"2015-01-22T22:11:43.680Z"},"homepage":"https://github.com/spoike/hubot-untappd","keywords":["hubot","beer","untappd","pub","chatbot"],"repository":{"type":"git","url":"https://github.com/spoike/hubot-untappd.git"},"author":{"name":"Mikael Brassman"},"bugs":{"url":"https://github.com/spoike/hubot-untappd/issues"},"license":"MIT","readmeFilename":"README.md"}
